  <name>Tesseract</name>
  <summary>Cubing in the fourth dimension</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A speed cubing timer, built with libcosmic and designed for simple but effective solve timing.
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Generate WCA compliant scrambles</li>
        <li>Time your solves with a StackMat style timer</li>
        <li>Keep track of your times and averages</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
